{"tid":300271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 又 打 錯 字 喇","createTime":"2017-06-27T17:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T18:29:00.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf381797fc50d4358c6b2f9a4a54a9bc46d4a3d","tid":300271,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"繼「食好西」、「海車雞」、「兩隻wife」同「「有無d停車場係免費或者女平㗎」後，今日又嚟一單。<br />\n<br />\n坤哥喺facebook問網民「激光叫視點睇」，由於個po係桃紅底襯白字，成件事，真係好搶眼！更搶嘅係，「激光叫視」&hellip;&hellip;講緊乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n再跟番「坤哥潮語錄」啲邏輯嚟推算，應該係講緊「激光矯視」，哦，咁就明晒！<br />\n正就正在，啲網民都自動tune到個台，明坤哥講乜，有開口叫坤哥改字嘅人，一隻手數得出。至於就坤哥個議題表態嘅，大部分人都覺得坤哥戴眼鏡好啲，仲話坤哥「副眼鏡係吉祥物，唔帶（戴）好似無咗個特別咁」，但亦有人贊成佢先做矯視，再戴番副平光眼鏡「保形象」。<br />\n其實坤哥會唔會考慮吓將自己啲潮語錄輯錄成書，可能有巿場嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498557769_33f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498557769_33f3.jpg&h=2f211f97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0adc16ba9a18d46052f7ca1cd2b7834a278a4d6b","tid":300271,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"1次好笑<br />\n2次戇鳩"},{"pid":"ea56b14e5becd0db3b6663bdc7cbb271a3845266","tid":300271,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"低質"},{"pid":"d1385c7b6b3c3002b07eb06b4974342a2c59505d","tid":300271,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"一個所謂藝人要靠打錯字上位<br />\n有幾多料心照啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542c3f37158626d045dba3c5c7153162a4fef186","tid":300271,"uid":8243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:29:00.000Z","msg":"打拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n如果唔係點會打錯矯同叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利伸：淨係識打筆畫</span